install node.js for npm
install npm install -g @angular/cli
Basic command to see if the angular cli is installed or not.
>ng -v 

Below command will start the new project 
> ng new <project-name> 
   -- necessary folder structure will be included by the angular CLI
   app.component.ts -> created by the cli
   app.module.ts-> created by the cli
   index.html -> the component selector name is marked as html tag.
   app.compnent.html -> can be used to provide more component.
